OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry and mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy day but with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells breaking through. Winds
OL,8,Fwill be light and feeling a little
OL,9,Fcooler than in recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA largely dry evening with
OL,12,Fperhaps the odd shower in the east and
OL,13,Fclear spells elsewhere. Dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith clear spells, leading to a cold
OL,15,Fnight and a frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FIt will be a largely dry day
OL,18,Fwith bright and sunny spells, the odd
OL,19,Fisolated shower possible however.
OL,20,FTurning cloudier in the evening with
OL,21,Frain spreading eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
